{"tid":968064,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界仔想上位]有聯儲局官員指未來數季應暫停加息","createTime":"2019-01-04T02:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T02:35:43.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"132557a95a3c6dfe04d8764a7549ff44f98e18c0","tid":968064,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=332959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D332959&d=pUPQkf61XcQGZPwxH5otPzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bfe4caec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D332959&h=497c9523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=332959</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】有美國聯儲局官員認為未來幾季應該暫停加息。<br />\n<br />\n達拉斯聯儲銀行行長卡普蘭表示，鑒於全球經濟增長前景不明朗，息口敏感的行業表現疲弱，連同金融狀況收緊，指聯儲局目前不應該採取任何貨幣政策行動，直至部分不明朗因素解決，認為今年首幾個季度都不應該加息。<br />\n<br />\n卡普蘭又表示，他沒有考慮過要減息，因為美國仍然有通脹，又表示在必要時聯儲局應該調整縮減資產負債表政策，即是放慢減持債券的步伐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}